Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Blackshield</b> was the identity taken by a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>.\n</p><p>Although his personal arms are not explicitly described, the knight's moniker suggests that his sigil was sable and uncharged.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blackshield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Blackshield participated as a mystery knight at a <a href=\"/index.php/History_of_Tourneys_in_Westeros#Oldtown_tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"History of Tourneys in Westeros\">tourney</a> held at <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> sometime between <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a>. He was unhorsed by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan the Bold</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, who unmasked him and revealed him as the <b>Bastard of Uplands</b>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Blackshield's given name is unknown. His surname is presumably \"Flowers\", the <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> name of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, as that is where <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mullendore\" title=\"House Mullendore\">House Mullendore</a>'s seat of <a href=\"/index.php/Uplands\" title=\"Uplands\">Uplands</a> is located.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blackshield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Chapter 67</a>, Jaime VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404195744\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.275 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 404/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10439/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5388/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 254/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  266.338      1 -total\n 95.72%  254.937      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.99%  252.982      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.0